<br>
        Welcome to The Casuals message board. There will not be a website, because Im to lazy to do that! I am a casual Everquest player hence it took a huge effort just to sign up for a message board!<br>
<br>
What kind of guild is The Casuals?<br>
<br>
      First and foremost we are not and never will be an &quot;Ubah&quot; Guild. Myself and maybe a few like minded folks play the game for amusement, fun and just to get away from real life occasionally. I do not have the time nor the inclination to play Everquest every night of the week, 5- 10 hours a night to become again what players call &quot;Ubah&quot;. I have no desire to obtain &quot;phat Loots&quot; ( Again I don't have the time nor the inclination to get to the zones with &quot;phat Loots&quot;). Will we Raid? Maybe or Maybe not, if we feel like it. If its not a fun time 'forget about it'.  I will log on to play a few hours, a few nights a week with online friends. I will slay monsters, help with a quest,sometimes just sit on my toons arse and chat, but its all in the name of fun. NO stress, no worries! There is no keeping up with Joneses(those are the stress-ors of real life which in my opinion do not belong in a game). What we do expect from our members? Of course they will be casual players and they have to be respectful to other gamers( No ks, ninja looting etc) and  follow the rules of the game ( no exploits,etc). And lastly they just want to have Fun in Norrath!! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :b --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":b"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br>
<br>
So by definition what are we?   ca·su·al   <br>
  Being without ceremony or formality; relaxed;  adj. Occurring by chance. <br>
<br>
So what will The Casuals do on Everquest Tonight? Whatever we want!!! <br>
<br>
Casually, <br>
              Katka Blackthorne <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://p214.ezboard.com/bthecasuals.showUserPublicProfile?gid=katkablackthorne>Katka Blackthorne</A> at: 9/6/04 7:00 pm<br></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://p214.ezboard.com/fthecasualsfrm1.showPrevMessage?topicID=1.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://p214.ezboard.com/fthecasualsfrm1.emailToFriend?topicID=1.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://p214.ezboard.com/fthecasualsfrm1.threadControl?topicID=1.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/slate/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://p214.ezboard.com/fthecasualsfrm1.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://p214.ezboard.com/fthecasualsfrm1.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to stop receiving email notification of replies"> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies</a> <br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://p214.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="thecasualsfrm1">Announcements<option value="thecasualsfrm2">General Discussion<option value="thecasualsfrm3">Polls<option value="thecasualsfrm4">Adm